Tripping Animals X B Fresh Gear? Say whattttt?

Back for round 3 with our favorite brewery from South Florida! Shoot, the only thing better than delicious beer is having some sweet gear to match!

       Let's talk exchanges and refunds!  Hygiene is important.  Good hygiene is even better!  Swimwear is designed to snuggle up right on the flesh, which means your private bits and crevices have probably been all up in that swimsuit.  Would you want to buy a garment that's been all up another persons areas? Probably not. Due to this notion, we cannot accept returns or exchanges on any swimwear that has been removed from its shrink wrapped packaging.  Sorry, but somebody has to look out for the germaphobes.  Please read the size chart carefully. 
 
 


Care instructions: 
Machine wash cold. 
Do not bleach. 
Always hang dry.

column2: 'I Saw The Sign' ASL - Fanny Pack
column3:
'I Saw The Sign' ASL awareness fanny pack. 

You heard that right! A fanny pack for a great cause. You might even say these fanny packs are packing some serious kindness! A portion of each sale is donated directly to the American American Society for Deaf Children. And if you're wondering why- because this is a near and dear cause to our team members and their families. 

Now! Fit check- does your bag or accessory allow you to b you? If it's B Fresh, then it most certainly does! 

Second question- does your bag or accessory tell a story? Well here's one for ya! 

Historians believe that sign language is much older than written or spoken language. The earliest evidence we have of communication through hand signs and gestures dates back to Greece in 5th century B.C.
One of the only culturally significant things that pre-dates sign language is the wearing of fanny packs! I think... 
At any rate- we can all agree that sign language and the wearing of fanny packs are both very kind gestures (just fill your fanny with shareable snacks and you'll know exactly what we mean!). So go forth with your new ASL awareness cross body bag and spread some kindness and awareness!

  • Portion of each sale donated to American Society For Deaf Children

column3:
I Saw The Sign! 

This is our limited edition, ASL Awareness stretch shirt. Proceeds from each purchase will go towards the American Society for Deaf Children. Not only that, each purchase helps raise awareness for our Deaf friends and family as well! Double Whammy!! 

And in case the cause alone isn't enough to peak your interest- check out this fun fact: 

 In 1894, a Deaf quarterback for Gallaudet University named Paul Hubbard invented the football huddle to covertly communicate his plays using American Sign Language, without the opposing team catching on.

Unfortunately, this short sleeve button down shirt wasn’t available until about 130 years later, but we are confident that if this Hawaiian shirt was around during his playing days, Paul would’ve been rocking it every chance he got! 

So grab one of these rad shirts, support an amazing cause, and remember- B kind, B you, and B Fresh!

In order to show your true hot dog eating, freedom loving patriotism, you’re gonna need to wear it on your chest! 

 Now, you’ve heard of honest Abe? Well his best friends knew him by a different name. They knew him to be an ass kickin, fist pumpin, beer slangin man of the people and they called him Abe Drinkin’. His infamous speech was actually mis-translated all those years ago. 

‘Four score and seven years ago’ is actually inaccurate. According to Abe- ‘seven years ago? The way the 1800’s health care was set up I can’t even remember 7 months ago!’. The real saying was ‘four score and seven beers ago!’. So yea, grab this leisurely patriotic shirt, crack a cold one, and let’s rewrite history!

Now that's something we can all plant our flag in.

Sometimes it's hot and sometimes it's not.

Sometimes you need a windbreaker jacket and sometimes you don't. 

This 90's windbreaker is made for those temperamental days where the weather can't make up it's damn mind!

Imagine leaving the house on a 75 degree day without a jacket cuz why the hell would I need a jacket if it's 75? And then BOOM, that temperamental little bish, The Weather, decides to start raining and the temp quickly drops to 50! 

Happened to you? Yea, me too!

That's why we at B fresh developed these very fresh fanny breakers. When it's 75 and sunny, you've got yourself a fanny pack with plenty of pocket space for your phone, keys and wallet. And then, when the Colorado weather decides to throw a tantrum, that fanny pack unfolds into a weather resistant windbreaker jacket.

Dress for any occasion and still b the best dressed! That's the B fresh lifestyle.

Features

  • Water and wind resistant nylon
  • Ribbed cuffs at the wrists and waist for tighter fit
  • YKK zippers
  • Kangaroo pouch with interior zippered pocket
  • Hand warmer pouch
  • Hood with drawstring
  • Fold into Fanny Pack with one exterior zippered pocket

Materials

Polyester

YKK Zippers

Fanny Pack ------> Stylish Weather Resistant Breaker

Probably not. Due to this notion, we cannot accept returns or exchanges on any swimwear that has been removed from its shrink wrapped packaging.  Sorry, but somebody has to look out for the germaphobes.  Please read the size chart carefully.

Sometimes it's hot and sometimes it's not.

Sometimes you need a windbreaker jacket and sometimes you don't. 

This 90's windbreaker is made for those temperamental days where the weather can't make up it's damn mind!

Imagine leaving the house on a 75 degree day without a jacket cuz why the hell would I need a jacket if it's 75? And then BOOM, that temperamental little bish, The Weather, decides to start raining and the temp quickly drops to 50! 

Happened to you? Yea, me too!

That's why we at B fresh developed these very fresh fanny breakers. When it's 75 and sunny, you've got yourself a fanny pack with plenty of pocket space for your phone, keys and wallet. And then, when the Colorado weather decides to throw a tantrum, that fanny pack unfolds into a weather resistant windbreaker jacket.

Dress for any occasion and still b the best dressed! That's the B fresh lifestyle.

Features

  • Water and wind resistant nylon
  • Ribbed cuffs at the wrists and waist for tighter fit
  • YKK zippers
  • Kangaroo pouch with interior zippered pocket
  • Hand warmer pouch
  • Hood with drawstring
  • Fold into Fanny Pack with one exterior zippered pocket

Materials

Polyester

YKK Zippers

Fanny Pack ------> Stylish Weather Resistant Breaker

It's not science, it's fashion.

Little know facts about Pandas.
- Pandas have 6 fingers
- Pandas do not hibernate
- Pandas are born pink
- Pandas can poop 28 kilos per day (that's 62lbs for you Americans)
- Pandas love Ice Cream
- Pandas love Beer.

Now, while some of these might just be hearsay, I think we can all agree that Pandas are the cutest, and if we could eat some ice cream, and drink a beer with one, that would be a long ass waitlist!

But there is one thing that comes close to being just as awesome. This Ice Cream Panda Capsule we created with our amazing friends from Tempe AZ at The Shop Beer CO. 

The Ice Cream Panda Beer is a Milkshake IPA with Lime, Coconut, and Pineapple. And is guaranteed to blow both of your socks clean OFF!

And would ya look at that, we've got a whole entire capsule to go right along with it!

As a designer, sometimes you just have to doodle! Sometimes those doodles are duds, but other times those doodles are dope! This doodle turned out dope! The Squiggles High Roller sunglasses.

The Squiggles just wanna wiggle! They're built for that action. Sports mode engaged! Three interchangeable, swappable lenses that help you go fast no matter what you do. Some of the best shades for beach volleyball, mountain biking, spring skiing, kayaking and more! Lightweight and durable with the coolest patterns around to get you those sweet sweet compliments!  And since you asked, here's the scoop on the three lenses included with each pair of Squiggles:

The first lens is UV400 and polarized with a big and bold purple revo coating! This lens is the statement lens the Squiggles come with! 

The second lens is also UV400 and polarized but is matte black for a more classic look.

The third lens is a sea-foam opaque lens that is UV400 but is not polarized. This lens is for low light activities- think playing sports on an overcast day. This lens is also the go to option for when you need to flex on em' and wear your sunglasses at night.

How to best describe the Big Fungus fanny pack? Well, it's clearly a super fresh ass fanny pack but besides that...

Let's roll play for a quick sec- If I see you at a show and your rocking the Big Fungus fanny pack by B fresh, and I approach you and ask, 'hey, what's in your fanny pack?' and without missing a beat you quickly reply, 'drugs.' then I'd venture to say that this particular fanny pack is THE perfect fanny pack for you! 

Chill out guys, it's not drugs if it's legal and we live in Colorady where a lot of stuff is now legal. What you put in this retro fanny pack after it crosses state lines is not the responsibility of B fresh gear. Tho we might cheer you on! 

Anyways, if you're a mushroom maniac, then this pack is probably also for you! The whole drug bit was just a joke. An accurate joke, but a joke nonetheless. 

Oh! And if you live in the midwest and go frolicking for Morel's, this fanny pack is DEFINITELY FOR YOU!! Plus, our fanny packs have four pockets so you can fit like 30 Morel's or so.

"A girlfriend who bought a b fresh reversible swimsuit kept getting called Psilocybin! Cuz all the guys were tripping while walking by it!' 

Careful ladies, this one takes you past the point of looking like a snack to looking like some delicious... extra curricular activities?! 
You're gonna love the Big Fungus double-sided swim suit if you love mushies like we think you do!
Reishi's (that's fashion), Lions Mane (that's focus), Cordyceps (that's compliments), Chaga (that's sexy), Turkey's Tail (that's sassy), and of course those whacky lil Psilocybin's (that's spiritual). It's a concoction of freshness and confidence! 
It's the type of statement piece that says 'I'm in control of this shit'! 

And let's not even get started on the flip side- our Nickel print which is sure to turn heads and accents too well with anything gold! 
So uh, yea- next time you fly to Vegas, ya best pack this luggage saver and get ready to trip out over the compliments! 

*Disclaimer* B fresh is not responsible for whatever may be offered to you on behalf of you wearing any of our garments which bare the Big Fungus design. 
In other words, you should only wear Big Fungus if you like to party. 



       Let's talk exchanges and refunds!  Hygiene is important.  Good hygiene is even better!  Swimwear is designed to snuggle up right on the flesh, which means your private bits and crevices have probably been all up in that swimsuit.  Would you want to buy a garment that's been all up another persons areas? Probably not. Due to this notion, we cannot accept returns or exchanges on any swimwear that has been removed from its shrink wrapped packaging.  Sorry, but somebody has to look out for the germaphobes.  Please read the size chart carefully.

Are you bald? No? Just fashion forward? 

Well whichever you are, wearing a bucket hat while doing sports under the hot sun is a really great way to protect your skin, stay cool, and look cool! And in a pinch, B fresh retro bucket hats are a great substitute to sunscreen (but we’re not dermatologists so you should probs still wear your sunscreen). 

And these particular reversible bucket hats are designed for the volleyball degenerates who know that the cold beer after the match is just as sweet as winning the match. Plus, they’re designed specially for the Emerald Coast FUD’s volleyball tournament which is like adult spring break. So this bucket hat will be like your keys to Ft Walton Beach twice a year when the tourney is under way. Just don’t tell the mayor…

If you have pockets full of crap while playing volleyball, guess what- you’re gonna have a bad time!

Those jingling keys are just gonna weigh you down and that wallet…? Forget about it! It already dropped out of your pocket and got buried by the sand in a quick shuffle of the feet. 

Now you’ve got lost property AND your jingling. Sounds like the nightmares infomercials are made of, doesn’t it!?

Well well well, we at B Fresh Gear have solved this problem for you! Introducing our four pocket, over-sized fanny pack designed specifically for volley ball players. It’s got a volleyball embroidered smack dab in the middle so you know it’s all about keeping your shiz together while you go out there and spike another broken nose! Yep. While you get your Focker on, this retro fanny pack will be sitting on the sidelines keeping all your belongings safe and dry. And free of sand too! 

Your phone, keys, and wallet will thank you once you safely store them in one of our awesome fannypacks.

You’ve been working on that hot bod in preparation for the years best beach volley ball tournament (no, I’m not talking about the Manhattan Beach 6 man). And the last thing you wanna do is cover up that chest once FUD’s arrives. Weather you’re rocking a 6 pack, or a 6 pack in the cooler, let that beautiful body show! 

But here’s the dilemma, you may or may not want to get sunburns and you may also want a rash guard for the sand. 

This shirt is the best of both worlds!

First of all it’s a button down so you can choose how much chest to show, or you can cover the whole damn pot roast up. 

Second, it’s made with s four way stretch spandex/poly blend so it’s made to move and stretch with you. In other words, the shirt is probably more athletic than you, especially after a night out at Fudpuckers. 

Best part, the design is official! Send a message to the opponents like ‘hey, not only am I serious about volleyball and fashion, I’m also here to drink your last beer after I spike you in the face!’

The limited edition FUD’s stretch shirt. Snag one now before they sell out.

Imagine dropping your date off and they invite you inside! Once you get through the front door they ask you to take your shoes off… and your dumb ass decided to rock socks with holes in em’?

Oh no pimpin’, that ain’t a good look at all. 

Sock check! 

Do your socks have holes in them? 

Yes? Toss them out immediately and shoot an email to help@bfreshgear.com so David can help you turn your life around ASAP! 

Ask for the ‘holeinmysock’ discount and tell him B sent ya. 

Sock check!

Do your socks match? 

No? C’mon now, we’re adults here. 

Believe it or not, mismatching socks don’t really add to your mystique or come across as unique. They kinda just make it look like your lazy with your laundry. So, if your socks don’t match, let’s go ahead and toss those out too. And yes, you may also email help@bfreshgear.com and explain to David that you’ve never had socks fresh enough to match; he’ll get you straightened out right away. 

Sock check!

Do your socks match anything else you’re currently rocking? 

No? Alright, that’s an easy fix! 

At B fresh, we’re rolling out a new initiative aimed at freshening up yo feet! 

You don’t have to walk 500 miles in my socks to get a thousand compliments, nah, all you gotta do is put them on! 

There’s a plethora of designs to choose from and guess what, every single pair has something else on the site to match it. Because yes pimp, we’re all about matchy matchy and accessorizing! 

These matching socks are the juice that’ll put the pep-in-yo-step! The proverbially rug that ties the whole room together. Ain’t no half stepping goin on in these B fresh socks. 

Like a treat for your feet! Fresh feet socks by B fresh gear. Cuz Ain’t no one got time for mismatched socks with holes in em’. 

So slap on a pair of our fresh feet socks and step out in style!

Keep your feet fresh!

Bear down on some essential storage space for all your outdoor activities! Hiking, Skiing, Kayaking? Where the mountain meets the road, an adventure awaits! And this fanny pack is equipped with enough pockets to help you keep all of your essentials right there on your hip.

Drive a Subaru? The Forester pack is for you. 

Have a Nalgene water bottle? The Forester pack is for you. 

Car keys and wallet? Front pocket. GPS enabled phone and portable charger in case you get lost and we need to find you? Second pocket. Pocket knife, toilet paper, first aid kit? Third pocket. Snacks and beer for the summit? Yup. Fourth pocket! 

The Forrester wants to be your adventure buddy. With a wilderness inspired design and a 53 inch waist band, these fanny packs pack a serious utilitarian punch. And when you flash this print to a bear, they won’t want to eat you, they’ll invite you back to the den to meet the family. 

Oh and one more thing, our signature fanny pack comes with YKK zippers so you won’t have a pocket jam when you’re 5 miles away from the car and in need of a quick snacky snack which is safely stored in your Forrester Fannypack.

column3:
We make fresh gear for people who drink good beer. 
 
As a fashion brand, there is so many different niches to choose from. Do we go after shuffle dancers or volley ball players? EDM lovers or country music fans? Well, we've made our top of the list decision! Craft Beer. 
Over the years, we’ve really gravitated towards the craft beer space for two main reasons! 
 
First, the beer! 
Delicious, delicious beer. 
 
Second, the people! 
Some of the most creative, inspired people we’ve met. 
Like us, many of them walked away from a stable job to risk it all in pursuits of a more passionate existence! 
 
We find that to B fresh AF! So we cooked up this limited edition design to celebrate this community for continually inspiring us to risk it all! 
Beer Bears is a yogi the bear, beer festival, craft beer inspired design! It’s featured on our four-way-stretch, button down dress shirt. Built to party and expand with a beer belly!

Sometimes it's hot and sometimes it's not.

This 90's windbreaker is made for those temperamental days where the weather can't make up it's damn mind!

Imagine leaving the house on a 75 degree day without a jacket cuz why the hell would I need a jacket if it's 75? And then BOOM, that temperamental little bish, The Weather, decides to start raining and the temp quickly drops to 50! 

Happened to you? Yea, me too!

That's why we at B fresh developed these very fresh fanny breakers. When it's 75 and sunny, you've got yourself a fanny pack with plenty of pocket space for your phone, keys and wallet. column3:
My nephew who is in Kindergarten designed this pack! No, seriously tho.

First, we got some construction paper and built a frame around it using some old plywood. Then we took a marble and dipped it in paint and rolled the marble around within the frame. First we did pink, then we did black, then we did blue. This print is the result! And it's perfect for a 90s style fanny pack! 

It came out so dope, I knew we had to use it! So we tossed it on a retro fanny pack, a bucket hat, a shirt, and a pair of shorts! Collect the fit and rock the 90's vibe. But this description is for the fanny packs so let’s get back to that fanny pack action. 

It has four awesomely utilitarian pockets so you can fit as many Fruit Roll Ups as you may or may not need!  It also has an adjustable belt that goes up to 53 inches in case you wind up eating all of those Fruit Roll Ups. 

And all of our fanny packs come equipped with YKK zippers so you’ll have no troubles getting to your… Fruit Roll Ups.

Now imagine they're on the same date and they forget sunscreen and they don't have their matching SPF shirts. You know what happens next? Disaster! Beach dates should always end with a romantic smash! Ever tried to smash with a sun burn? Yea- no fly zone there bud. 

So get yourself The Max SPF shirt, avoid the burns, and to get smashing! Pro tip- if you're smashing on the beach, keep your SPF shirt on so you don't get all sandy! They're made with a polyester/spandex blend so they actually feel great against your skin.

The beach is calling! That warm weather and those cool blue waves. And what about the beach volley ball? Yea, you know you want to get down on some volley action on the beach! 

But before you say yes to those beachside volley ball plans, you’re going to need somewhere to stash your belongings! Can’t be out there on the courts with a pocket full of crap weighing down your vert. 

That’s why we created these four pocket fanny packs with more room than you’re going to need for those pocket essentials. We’re talking phone, keys, wallet, sunscreen, AND snacks… and maybe a few shooters too if that floats your bumbag? 

This particular fanny pack is designed specifically for our volley ball fam. Featuring a fun print of Gators and Leopards going at it, digging it out of the sand and spiking it in the opponents face! 

To be real, this pattern was specifically inspired by the Fuds tournament in Ft. Walton Beach, Florida. A magical event that happens twice a year and brings together some of the coolest and most rad people we’ve ever met! So grab a retro hip pack and hit the beach with us this spring for another epic volley ball tournament!

Grandma's Couch Pearl Snap Western Shirt -

Grandma had a big family! Probably cuz she needed a lot of ranch hands. She needed at least 6 hands out in the field and at least 2 hands helping her prepare the meals and keep the ranch-hands cloths in good form. Grandma couldn't afford to sew shirts but once in a blue moon so always searched the markets for something durable. Then she found the perfect pearl snap shirts. These shirts are 90 double twill polyester, and 10% cotton. They're rugged, they're durable, they're clean! Colorado Cowboys and Cowgirls are rough, rugged, and indulgent. This vintage ski vest is designed for you, Coloradan! This vintage ski vest is tough like you, Coloradan! That's why it has no sleeves. You know, suns out guns out? So what if it's below 10 and windy, that Rocky Mountain sun is still shining! That's why this vest popped its sleeves off in true slammer fashion. This B Fresh Gear Vintage Ski Vest is comprised of a nylon shell, nylon lining and an unsuspectingly warm polyester filling! The Coloradan has been first down the mountain so many times it can afford to let the 77' win a few. It's aware of its power and remains confident! Whether you're a unicorn or a transplant, show your Colorado pride with this rare find.

Catch the vapors, not wind burn! 

This iconic 1980's style windbreaker will break so much wind, people will start saying excuse you! To which you can reply 'pardon my drip'. 

Did you just break wind? Society’s most embarrassing accusation. Rest assured, now you can look your accusers dead in the eye and proclaim, “YES, yes I did!". I had everything packed neatly inside and I decided to let it rip... Check out my cool windbreaker! It’s not just a dope retro jacket either, this thing is packable!"

The 90’s was vibrant! Colorful! Often geometric and sometimes splattered or sponged. Whatever the application, the 90’s was colorful and bold! Perhaps the best visual representation of the 90’s can be seen in the carpet that lined our favorite venues' floors back in the day. My school, famous video, the movie theater, TILT arcade… IT WAS EVERYWHERE! And it was damn inspiring. It made every place you went feel like K.B. toy store. It dared us to color outside the lines! To wear loud *ss patterns and bright ass colors if we wanted to. Bottom line- carpet taught us to be expressive! To pay our respects to the era with the best carpet laying skills of all time- we created the 90’s splatters! Inspired by loud ass carpet patterns! Shout out to Portland International Airport! This is a rare space that has been preserved in time. If you want to know how it feels to stand on abstract greatness, go take a walk thru the PDX carpet garden! You’ll find us there wearing our 90’s splatters laying some carpet. Now that’s what we call market research! 

Features

  • Polarized lenses
  • UV-400 Protective
  • Splatter paint print
  • Includes Matching Sunglasses Cord
  • Inspired by carpet

column3:
Retro Beach / Van Dope Reversible Swimwear One Piece!

              You're here because you want to make a splash this summer! You've been working out and eating right and now you need the perfect b fresh bathing-suit to match your style and reward your hard work. Look no further, you found it! Twice. This ladies reversible swimwear is reversible. Retro Beach is for those neon nights while Van Dope is for those sunny water slides! Van Dope crushes pool-side bottomless mimosas while Retro Beach gets dinner paid for. What we're trying to say is; with two ridiculously awesome prints, this suit is twice as nice. That means 4X the compliments! Go ahead, slip into this reversible swimsuit and then slip into it again! You deserve it! 
       Let's talk exchanges and refunds!  Hygiene is important.  Good hygiene is even better!  Swimwear is designed to snuggle up right on the flesh, which means your private bits and crevices have probably been all up in that swimsuit.  Would you want to buy a garment that's been all up another persons areas? Probably not. Due to this notion, we cannot accept returns or exchanges on any swimwear that has been removed from its shrink wrapped packaging.  Sorry, but somebody has to look out for the germaphobes.  Please read the size chart carefully. 
 
 
Care instructions: 
Machine wash cold. 
Do not bleach. 
Always hang dry.

And of course we tossed in them retro palm trees and and some retro squiggles for good measure.  Toucan Sam now has the dopest pair of swimtrunks in the Atlantic ocean! Be like Toucan Sam and get yerself a pair of these retro beach swim trunks. You'll improve your shotgunning speeds, have the best diving board tricks at the pool, and they'll most likely get you laid. For a full block out, you've got the fully reflective, polarized, UV400 pink lens. Once mom starts calming her sh*t down, you can switch the pinks out for the polarized, UV400 gradient smoke lens. Those will block out what you don't want, but will also allow the good vibes in. Then, once mom is fully cool again, you can switch it up to the clear lenses and go full send on that jet ski knowing you've got the proper eye protection in place! There's levels to this. Plus, the Sun Blocker sports sunglasses are athletic enough to bail before Dad sinks the water craft.

It’s fourth grade and the bell just rang. You grab your book bag and rendezvous with your walking home crew. It’s nineteen ninety something and you ain’t worried about a thing! You get home and smell those after school snacks already cooking in the oven. Delicious! Pizza rolls in hand, you call dibs on the recliner and pop the T.V. onto channel 3. You’ve just invited  DJ Jazzy Jeff and the Fresh Prince of Bel Air into your living room for a party! Psssh…

Throw the Fresh Prints reversible vest on and relive the hype with your very own 90’s fashion statement. It’s like hanging with Mr. Cooper and eating Danny Tanners cookies at the same time! The Fresh Prints puffy vest brings the nostalgia! 

Our authentic geometric pattern coupled with an inspired color palette represents the balance and tradition of 90’s culture. And then there’s the black accent and opaque snap buttons which make this vest crackle and pop! Or, if you want to turn the volume down a bit, flip the vest over and let the geometric pattern accent the black nylon shell. Two parties, one vest. If you do party like it’s 99', send us your address and we’ll show up with your Fresh Prints reversible vest!

Wacka Flocka Flamingos Reversible Swimwear One Piece!
 
What happens when two flamingos walk into a porthole set for the early 90's?  They wind up on a silky smooth, totally radical, reversible women's one piece swim suit; that's what! 
         This piece features a collaboration between our favorite new age nostalgic artists. Tight!  To be more redundantly clear, this retro bathing suit features another nostalgic bathing suit. One side is the @wackaworld 'Wacka Flocka Flamingos' print while the other side is the @tomabbisssmithart 'Into the Abbiss' design.  That's a double whammy on totally awesome sporty swimwear, tight... TIGHT!  It's actually the perfect amount of tight. The spandex gives you a nautical hug while the polyester keeps you shimmering in the sun!
Abstract meets everyone's favorite bird of paradise meets B Fresh Gear!  The result?  Best. Dressed. Every time!
 
 
Let's talk exchanges and refunds!  Hygiene is important.  Good hygiene is even better!  Swimwear is designed to snuggle up right on the flesh, which means your private bits and crevices have probably been all up in that swimsuit.  Would you want to buy a garment that's been all up another persons areas? Probably not. Due to this notion, we cannot accept returns or exchanges on any swimwear that has been removed from its shrink wrapped packaging.  Sorry, but somebody has to look out for the germaphobes.  Please read the size chart carefully. 
 
 
Care instructions: 
Machine wash cold. 
Do not bleach. 
Always hang dry.

How to make a splash!
     
Search MySpace for the most happening pool party in your immediate area. Crash it!  Show up with your 'Into the Abbiss' retro swim trunks and an empty piñata. This is your ticket past any security detail, no matter how tight.  Once in, make note of the food situation and locate the bar. Next, stake out your real estate.  You'll want the best poolside spot with plenty of sunshine.  Bring your David Hasselhoff beach towel.  In the event that your spot is taken, simply throw the double guns, whip your towel from around your waist exposing your 'Into the Abbiss' nostalgic swim trunks, cock your chin and say, 'Names Bronze, LeBronze James'.  If your spot is fit for a king, this should open it right up.  Once you have your chaise lounge secured, oil up those buns baby!  Lather it on and show off your leBronze.  Cook for 30-45 minutes or until someone approaches you and asks whom you received your invite from.  Tell them your Jack's cousin in from Jersey City.  At this point you'll want to offer the piñata.   Tell them it's stuffed with shooters! They'll be stoked that you didn't come empty handed.  While the hosts are busy trying to hang the piñata, you'll want to sneak in your swim.
  
The diving board is obviously the best way to make a splash!  The trick is up to you.  We suggest the classic cannon ball, nothing Hokie like a pencil dive nose plug.  Now that you're in the pool enjoying your super dope bathing-suit, keep a close eye on the piñata, you'll have about 10 minutes until people start taking whacks at it.  During this time, grab a floaty and enjoy your pool session, this is what you came to do!  When the piñata is ready, you'll surely be offered the first whack. Whilst in the pool, kindly insist that someone else go first.  At this point you'll want to end your swim.  Head for the food and bar.  You've got about 10 whacks left.  Help yourself to a bottle or two of the most expensive booze present and grab one of the pizzas.  Casually walk towards the exit.  You should be about three quarters the way towards the exit when the piñata rips open and nothing comes out.  Once you reach the gate, you'll have been exposed as the classless party crashing jabronie that you are. Enjoy a seamless escape! No slippage thanks to the fast drying retro swim trunks you're sporting. Leave the Hasselhof towel behind, you've got a linen closest full of them.
